title: Senior center names royalty
maintext:
Submitted photo
Royalty: The Central City Senior Center crowned their queen, Theresa Alexander, and king, Jim Williams, on Feb. 14. Seniors were given a Valentine’s heart with chocolates. The royalty also received a gift from the center.
